<html i18n:domain="iw.subscriber"
      tal:define="mfrom options/mfrom;
                  email options/email;
                  crypted options/crypted;
                  brains options/brains;">
    <head>
      <div tal:replace="structure provider:plone.htmlhead" />
      <style type="text/css">
        .unsubscribe {
          float:right;
          font-size:80%;
        }
      </style>
    </head>
    <body>
	  <div>
	    <p>Vous trouverez ci-dessous les dossiers auxquels vous êtes abonnés
		leurs contenus récemment modifiés.
        </p>
		<p>Here are the folders which you have subscribed to and
		their recently modified contents.
		</p>
	  </div>
      <div tal:repeat="value brains/items">
        <tal:define tal:define="brain python:value[0];
                                values python:value[1];">
        <h3>
          <a tal:content="brain/Title"
             tal:attributes="href brain/getURL">
            Title
          </a>
        </h3>
        <a i18n:translate=""
           class="unsubscribe"
           tal:attributes="href string:${brain/getURL}/unsubscribe_form.html?v=$crypted">Unsubscribe</a>
        <p class="documentDescription"
           tal:condition="brain/Description"
           tal:content="brain/Description">
           Description
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li tal:repeat="brain values">
            <a tal:content="brain/getURL"
               tal:attributes="href brain/getURL">
              url
            </a>
			<span tal:content="brain/Title">
			Title
			</span>
            <p class="documentDescription"
               tal:condition="brain/Description"
               tal:content="brain/Description">
               Description
            </p>
          </li>
        </ul>
        </tal:define>
      </div>
    </body>
</html>